description:
Marilyn Manson - Long is the Way, and Hard, That Out of Hell Leads Up to Light


A modest Marilyn Manson compilation. For the most part it stays clear of the singles and the more well-known songs. Because how many more times do you need to hear "The Beautiful People" and "I Don't Like The Drugs But The Drug Like Me"? No more times, is the correct answer.

1. Irresponsible hate anthem (1996)
2. This is the new shit (2003)
3. Overneath the path of misery (2012)
4. Doll-dagga buzz-buzz ziggety- zag (2003)
5. Little horn (1996)
6. Dope hat (1994)
7. President dead (2000)
8. Sweet dreams (1995)
9. The gardener (2012)
10. Get your gunn (1994)
11. I want to disappear (1998)
12. Ka-boom ka-boom (2003)
13. Angel with the scabbed wings (1996)
14. You and me and the devil makes 3 (2007)
15. Murderers are getting prettier every day (2012)
16. The death song (2000)
17. We're from America (2009)
18. King kill 33 (2000)
19. 1996 (1996)
20. Count to six and die (2000)
